<div data-controller="timer">
  <div class="main-card time-space">

    <h2 class="header-text">Your Dragon Glass Timer</h2>
    <p>
In the mystical land of Pomodorania, where dragons roamed and productivity thrived, the Dragon's Hourglass was forged from the fiery breath of a time-obsessed dragon, ensuring that tasks were conquered with a sizzling determination. </p>

      <div class="time-background">

          <div class="counter-container justify-content-center">
            <div class="time-container">
              <div class="minutes" data-timer-target="minutes">25</div>
              <div><p>:</p></div>
              <div class="seconds" data-timer-target="seconds">00</div>
            </div>
            <div class=timer-buttons>
              <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#appTimer">Start</button>
              <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#pauseTimer">Pause</button>
              <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#stopTimer">Stop</button>
            </div>
        </div>



          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <div class="counter-container d-flex justify-content-center flex-column">
              <h5 class="timer-header">Your Break Time</h5>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="minutes" data-timer-target="minutesB">5</div>
                <div><p>:</p></div>
                <div class="seconds" data-timer-target="secondsB">00</div>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex justify-content-around">
                <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#appBreak">Start</button>
                <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#pauseBreak">Pause</button>
                <button class="btn-fant" data-action="click->timer#pauseBreak">Stop</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      <div>
  </div>
</div>


